uwu-vibe contains an independent Rust implementation of the documented Wooting
analog and RGB HID protocols. Protocol details were derived from Wooting's
official open-source SDKs, which are licensed under MPL-2.0:

- https://github.com/WootingKb/wooting-analog-sdk
- https://github.com/WootingKb/wooting-rgb-sdk

